Package: pymds
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python-ipaddr
Description: Python-based modular DNS authoritative nameserver
 pymds is a Python-based, modular DNS server.
 .
 One of its neat features is a backend for automatically faking
 forwards and reverse entries for IPv6 addresses.
